                     "<li style='color:blue;'><strong>Their</strong> Connections with Other than themselves (whether humans or things)</li>"+
                     "<li><strong>Their</strong> View of the World</li>"+
                     "<li><strong>Their</strong> Physical Activities</li>"+
                     "</ul>",
